§0Pg.23-25 Local News
#- International News§0
§0------------------- Dust settles as peace is declared.§0
§0
§0 The Chimeria Alliance quickly fell apart when Volterra broke into the Ruin vault almost a week ago. The server was tense in what seemed to be§0

#- International News§0
§0------------------- a very long lasting stalemate. However when the war seemed to be drawing closer to "an end" both sides discovered what they thought to be a covert 3rd party. Supposedly members of Cantina and Bigdogs§0

#- International News§0
§0------------------- had a plot to destroy Volterra, Ruin, and NewVeritas. Then to take over the rest of Devoted. Although at first this sounded like a crude conspiracy, it drove Volterra, Ruin & NV to swiftly sign a peace treaty.
#- International News§0
§0------------------- Cantina was then attacked and many of their citizens were pearled. Many of the remaining Bigdogs (Who divided up into both sides at the beginning of the war) were also pearled. Before the war Cantina was known to
#- International News§0
§0------------------- harbor pearled players "seasonally" usually during major conflicts. It was a city of exiles. Cwage who we covered last edition was once again pearled in this conflict after being freed days before from Iria.§0

#- International News§0
§0------------------- Cwage is now taking a "break". Volterra, Ruin, and NewVeritas are now functioning normally. TheJKH now describes Volterra 'Taking Pride in Politics, Friendship, and aspiring to extraordinary things.' §0

#- International News§0
§0------------------- The Vogelburg post is waiting for offical comments reguarding Cwage's pearl being held. We hope new information is released on the matter very soon. We also hope more information from offical sources is released.
#- Follow Up Story§0
§0------------------- Cwaged claimed Xinteng used him§0
§0
§0 Last edition we wrote an article about Cwage, who claimed that Clara (Former Xinteng Leader) had used him. By making him mine for long periods of time
#- Follow Up Story§0
§0------------------- with little in return.§0
§0These claims at the time appeared to be very alleged. However they were backed up by an independent source who was unaware of Cwage's claims. Clara was eventually removed 
#- Follow Up Story§0
§0-------------------§0
§0 in an Xinteng coup. Anon00014 and John3112 now run Xinteng which was recently renamed to Iria. It appears Clara may also be taking a break from devoted now too. 
#- Main Story§0
§0-------------------Persia says goodbye§0
§0
§0We heard reports that Persia ended itself. Tomocat made a reddit post "Final Destruction of Persiapolis" Tomo and other citizens feared an invasion by,
#- Main Story§0
§0-------------------NewVeritas, Ruin and Volterra. This was because Persia lent the city to Viccy who was caught up in the supposed 3rd party in the Volterra V. Chimeria war. This 3rd party was supposedly trying to plot
#- Main Story§0
§0------------------- aganist Volterra and Chimeria. We sent some journalists to access the Perisan destruction. When we arrived we had trouble exiting the railstation and eveverything was greifed with reinforced blocks.§0

#- Main Story§0
§0-------------------Xurksice (Pre-Coup Persian leader) called this a "dick move". The_DonaldTrump a former offical of Solaria/Persia is planning to rehab the city. He's calling for §0
§0anyone on Dev 3.0 to help him. According to
#- Main Story§0
§0-------------------§0
§0The_Donald those who help clear the greif will recieve a plot for a house in Persia. It remains unclear if MTA will back the PersExit. The_Donald seems ready to move ahead nonetheless. He is very determined
#- Main Story§0
§0------------------- to fix up Persia. We asked SerraNova (MTA Mayor) what would happen if a PersExit occured. They replied saying 'MTA at heart is a peaceful place, where many viewpoints coexist.' Serra went on speaking of peace.
#- Main Story§0
§0------------------- Serra hopes that MTA and New-Perisan officals can reconcile and also said that no force is necessary from either sides. Serra also said that this is nothing for other foreign nations to get involved with.
#- Sub Story A.§0
§0------------------- Akkala joins Byzanchan§0
§0
§0 Akkala has joined the Byzanchan empire. Byzanchan has been strengthing it's alliances in the North West. Akkala has been an ally of Byzanchan 
#- Sub Story A.§0
§0------------------- quite some time now, so it's not a huge suprise that they've decided to join Byzanchan. The UFoN is also a new North Western Nation that is also starting to form alliances with Akkala and Chan-Nations.
#- Sub Story B.§0
§0------------------- UF and UFoN§0
§0
§0Two new nations have joined Devoted. The United Federation (UF) a self proclaimed democratic republic, and The United Federation of Normandy (UFoN)
#- Sub Story B.§0
§0------------------- The UFoN has a more Nationalistic approach to their government. Both Nations share very similar names. These nations are almost the anthesis of each other, but share excruciating similar names.
#- Local News!§0
§0------------------- AidanVonLoopy Returns!§0
§0
§0King Aidanvonloopy has returned to Vogelburg. They were away for awhile when the king steped down for IRL reasons. However it was only for a short 
#- Local Cont'd§0
§0------------------- 3-4 Month period. While that period took place a lot of wars broke out. Including the Big Dogs crisis which heavily affected Vogelburg. We're excited to see what Aidanvonloopy plans to do now that their back.
#- Local Cont'd§0
§0------------------- Coming into Vogelburg we saw a grand Railstation built by Retyu. The railstation was built under Jamietech's Administration. We hope to see even more projects like this in VB and Dev 3.0.
#- The Vogelburg Post!§0
§0-------------------  We try to keep the Newspapers cost low to make news affordable to everyone and not just the one percent. We do however need donations to keep running! Please contact citylion to donate anything else!
